{"tid":815353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「都係一句，保唔保安不是重點，最重要支付工具要派錢！」","createTime":"2018-09-12T03:53:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T07:37:37.000Z","uid":144113,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ed853a8dbeb24d2d611a7d0fcc987daed9bca049","tid":815353,"uid":144113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T03:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/12/115226_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F12%2F115226_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2366c45d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n完美體現香港豬嘅心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔怪得支那寶, we7pay喺香港傳播得咁快，係錢呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da8978c6f42ed4eb723a7de93d87ff715eb85d6","tid":815353,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T03:55:20.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"1266b35b50149034ef81e9d0bd268a3c415b771e","tid":815353,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T03:56:03.000Z","msg":"騙徒手法十年如一, 總有人自願中招<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phptDdCIG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phptDdCIG.jpg&h=32d53761&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕有中國商人指出，即將在台灣推出「掃碼換面紙」的活動，讓民眾透過手機掃描面紙機上的QR code，就能領取從機器內掉出的1包面紙，不過，同時也會讓業者取得手機內的資訊。<br />\n<br />\n臉書粉絲專頁「由台商变（變）台傷」今（9）日PO出2張照片，從中能夠清楚看見2台不同造型的面紙機，它們有別於一般的面紙機要投入10元才能換得2包面紙，民眾只要開啟手機掃碼功能，掃描機上的QR code，就能得到1包面紙，且每天都能夠換1包面紙。<br />\n<br />\n不過，該粉絲專頁警告，拿免費面紙也是要付出代價的，中國商人計畫要把此種機台大舉引入台灣，讓民眾於各大賣場、商店或公共場所，都能「掃碼換面紙」，但同時民眾手機內包括個資在內的資訊，亦全數為業者所有，令許多台灣網友感到相當不安。<br />\n<br />\n有網友認為這項活動實為「個資換面紙」，其他網友們紛紛留言指出「個資只值一包面紙？」、「有某國人為了方便可以犧牲隱私」、「這好像是問老鴇還有沒有貞操一樣」、「那地方還有隱私嗎」、「應該很多人會去領」、「佔小便宜、永遠不知下一秒是否會失大虧」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/2420852\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F2420852&d=0ae027bs3124tcF0V6cgnCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=0f0c8d2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F2420852&h=62fa6985\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/2420852</a>"},{"pid":"b9aadb5d51da51aa64e2b8127b4d6a649e0e4d35","tid":815353,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T03:56:41.000Z","msg":"HK$20買晒手機入面會部DATA<br />\n<br />\n抵到爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a2e460061f8f735ed20f093616e35a01ad3f22","tid":815353,"uid":144113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:02:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7879aac889a6fa9350860fceab0ab98f7a658fe3","tid":815353,"uid":7854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:03:16.000Z","msg":"最天真既莫過於以為自己D資料好安全<br />\n<br />\n支那只要講一聲 林奠乜都雙手奉上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc9130f1a61d9711a8fc76b5f45d56bd7d26afc8","tid":815353,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:08:53.000Z","msg":"首階段「銀聯雲閃付」手機 App 支援的香港銀行包括：中國銀行（香港）、交通銀行（香港）<br />\n<br />\n好人好姐都唔用會呢2種垃圾BANK<br />\n同埋我PAYWAVE 拍一拍一秒就得，屌你老母又要開APP又要掃，要柒幾多獲支那人先會肯用NFC"},{"pid":"568a83e24f6b937615360d78cbeeedf88443281a","tid":815353,"uid":144113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T06:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6856879a987b825740348a5166264c0bbf28205e","tid":815353,"uid":30633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T07:11:21.000Z","msg":"當中國幫你建立&quot;個人社會積分&quot; <br />\n已經不是一般保安問題咁簡單...."},{"pid":"653f0b3aa1621a65